-bt-override-class=\"null\"><\/div><\/div><\/div><div  class=\"bt_bb_column col-md-6 col-sm-12 bt_bb_align_right bt_bb_vertical_align_top bt_bb_animation_fade_in zoom_out animate bt_bb_padding_normal bt_bb_animation_fade_in bt_bb_animation_zoom_out animate\"  data-width=\"6\"><div class=\"bt_bb_column_content\"><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"bt_bb_row_wrapper\"><div  class=\"bt_bb_row\"  data-bt-override-class=\"{}\"><div  class=\"bt_bb_column col-md-12 col-ms-12 bt_bb_align_left bt_bb_vertical_align_top bt_bb_animation_fade_in move_up animate bt_bb_padding_normal bt_bb_animation_fade_in bt_bb_animation_move_up animate\"  data-width=\"12\"><div class=\"bt_bb_column_content\"><div class=\"bt_bb_separator bt_bb_border_style_none bt_bb_bottom_spacing_normal bt_bb_hidden_md bt_bb_hidden_lg\" data-bt-override-class=\"null\"><\/div><div class=\"bt_bb_separator bt_bb_border_style_none bt_bb_bottom_spacing_normal bt_bb_hidden_md bt_bb_hidden_lg\" data-bt-override-class=\"null\"><\/div><div  class=\"bt_bb_text\" ><p style=\"direction: ltr; text-align: left;\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-3706 size-medium\" src=\"https:\/\/drassat.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/image17-640x330.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"330\" srcset=\"https:\/\/drassat.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/image17-640x330.jpg 640w, https:\/\/drassat.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/image17-1280x659.jpg 1280w, https:\/\/drassat.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/image17-768x396.jpg 768w, https:\/\/drassat.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/image17-320x165.jpg 320w, https:\/\/drassat.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/image17.jpg 1320w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" \/><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<li style=\"direction: ltr;\"><b>Already in business, but the vision is blurry?<\/b><\/li>\n<li><strong>Is the market changing around?<\/strong><\/li>\n<li><strong>Want a structured way to understand what clients want?<\/strong><\/li>\n<li><strong>Or didn\u2019t start your business and don\u2019t have a clear vision of how to operate? The<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>A business plan is a blueprint that defines the major elements of running a business, initiative, or project as it gives answers to questions like:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\n<ul>\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\n<ul>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">What kind of resources are needed?<\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: left;\">What are the lines of communication and the detailed organizational structure?<\/li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">What are marketing activities and tactics required to achieve goals?<\/li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">What is the action plan to carry out the strategy, and what are the Key Performance Indicators -KPI?<\/li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">What is the overall financial plan &amp; financial assessment for the upgrade plan?<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>A business plan is usually subcategorized into the marketing plan, the human resources plan, the operational plan, and the financial plan.<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><!--more--><\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section><section id=\"bt_bb_section63f39a610d658\"  class=\"bt_bb_section bt_bb_top_spacing_medium bt_bb_bottom_spacing_medium bt_bb_layout_boxed_1200 bt_bb_vertical_align_top\" style=\";background-color:#18407c;\"><div class=\"bt_bb_port\"><div class=\"bt_bb_cell\"><div class=\"bt_bb_cell_inner\"><div class=\"bt_bb_row_wrapper\"><div  class=\"bt_bb_row\"  data-bt-override-class=\"{}\"><div  class=\"bt_bb_column col-md-12 col-ms-12 bt_bb_align_left bt_bb_vertical_align_top bt_bb_animation_fade_in move_up animate bt_bb_padding_normal bt_bb_animation_fade_in bt_bb_animation_move_up animate\"  data-width=\"12\"><div class=\"bt_bb_column_content\"><div class=\"